<collectingCountry box="[192,275,898,922]" name="South Korea" pageId="11" pageNumber="10">Korea</collectingCountry>
quarantine notes
</emphasis>
. This species was intercepted 12 times; Indonesia, Malaysia, Philippines, Vietnam, China (
<emphasis box="[404,522,930,953]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="10">Dracaena</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
